Package com.foreach.across.modules.dynamicforms.domain.definition.types

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DynamicTypeDefinition
    Represents a type definition, for example: single value string multi value integer selectable list of values A type definition has a java type representation.
    DynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder
    Represents a builder for a single type definition.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DocumentDynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder
    A DynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder for a type that refers to a specific DynamicDocument or DynamicDocumentVersion.
    DynamicDataFieldSet
    Specialized type that represents a fieldset type in a dynamic document.
    DynamicDataFieldSetTemplateRegistry
    Registry that holds the registered templates for ViewElementFieldsets.
    DynamicDataFieldSetToStringConverter
    Converts a DynamicDataFieldSet to String by converting it to JSON.
    DynamicTypeDefinitionFactory
    Responsible for creating GenericDynamicTypeDefinition instances.
    EntityDynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder
    A DynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder for a type that refers to another entity registered in the EntityRegistry.
    EnumDynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder
    A DynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder for an enumeration type.
    EnumDynamicTypeOptions
    Represents the set of possible values allowed for an enum type.
    FieldsetDynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder
    A DynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder for a fieldset type.
    FileDynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder
    A DynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder that supports file uploads via FileReference properties.
    GenericDynamicTypeDefinition
    Generic implementation of a DynamicTypeDefinition.
    GenericDynamicTypeDefinition.GenericDynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder  
    SimpleDynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder
    A DynamicTypeDefinitionBuilder for the following standard types: string text boolean number

    This builder usually comes last.
